title: Super Cheesy Cauliflower Pasta Bake with Plant-Based Basil Pesto & Cherry Tomato Salad
description: Golden, oozey and irresistibly crispy, this cauliflower pasta bake is pure comfort food bliss! Packed with both Parmesan and Cheddar cheese, a touch of plant-based basil pesto and served with a bright cherry tomato salad, it’s a creamy-crunchy dream come true.
